{"tid":945743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【韓流】離港航班延誤一小時 Wanna One粉絲追到上飛機？","createTime":"2018-12-18T06:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T06:22:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f58d543759ea4b99cc9b530df0b5d7f8bf8958e5","tid":945743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181216/59037104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181216%2F59037104&d=%2F8IpAWi2c54X29EX9Mi5WpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e42d6496\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181216%2F59037104&h=dfcc446f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181216/59037104</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年12月16日 <br />\n<br />\n【韓流】離港航班延誤一小時 Wanna One粉絲追到上飛機？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181216/large/1544958697_63ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181216%2Flarge%2F1544958697_63ed.jpg&h=2e6fd298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑似係Wanna One嘅粉絲，噚日於禁區及飛機上見完偶像後，要求落機及退票。<br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1216 20:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓國人氣男團Wanna One日前來港出席韓國年度音樂盛事《MAMA音樂頒獎禮》，噚日下午Wanna One就由香港飛返韓國，吸引大批粉絲送機，而Wanna One入到禁區後，粉絲更好似韓片《屍殺列車》咁跑晒過去禁區前望多偶像一面，場面墟冚。<br />\n<br />\n而據韓媒報道，噚日就有4名疑似係Wanna One嘅粉絲，為於禁區內見偶像而買機票，等到Wanna One登機後，就以有急事為由要求落機及退票。機組人員基於保安理由而要全機乘客落機及重新接受安檢，令飛機延遲一小時先起飛，機上360名乘客因而受影響。據知4名要求落機嘅乘客，當中包括一名香港人，另外三人係中國籍乘客。<br />\n<br />\n精選韓流，喺晒《娛果》<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyen&d=%2F8IpAWi2c54X29EX9Mi5WpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=fe38dd60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyen</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181216/large/1544958706_c488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181216%2Flarge%2F1544958706_c488.jpg&h=8ef50502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n噚日大批粉絲去送機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181216/large/1544958706_e6be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181216%2Flarge%2F1544958706_e6be.jpg&h=4bea3283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWanna One噚日下午離港<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n相關閱讀<br />\n<br />\n如何近距離接觸偶像？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/945740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/945740</a>"},{"pid":"3046854a16c834d02409efc1e96b70a254edb1c2","tid":945743,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T06:22:53.000Z","msg":"泡狗腦殘是常識吧......"}]}